15 Hours Ago The building collapsed around 3.30pm on Saturday. He said the site had been sealed off twice before the collapse. “However, the developer later broke government seal, sneaked into the site and re-commenced construction without official authorisation. “The developer in charge of the site has since been arrested and handed over to the RRS Team, while rescue operation is ongoing,” the statement said.